summary: This dispatch concerns the identification of Manuel ESTEVEZ Perez by AMMUG/1. AMMUG/1 was unable to identify the name. It suggests providing a photograph of the subject to HAVE to show AMMUG/1 for possible identification.
title: AMMUG/1 Identification of Manuel ESTEVEZ Perez
recipient: Chief of Station, Madrid; Chief of Base, Barcelona; Chief of Station, JMWAVE
